{"tid":459100,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（致日校學生）（有圖）記住擦鞋 爆sba 否則後悔一世","createTime":"2017-11-05T13:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T11:45:39.000Z","uid":143307,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"84299ab549def65389a78c618fac922af405b100","tid":459100,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"先前已經有張一貼論sba重要性<br />\n就快到上交sba分時間<br />\n忠告所有考生<br />\n<br />\n話唔重要嘅只係3種人<br />\n1.神人 就算sba0分都完爆所有正常人<br />\n2.既得利益者 技不如人靠sba拉grade 然後死要面撐唔重要<br />\n3.教畜 為咗敷衍你 話sba跟公開試呃x你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">SBA隨時要你命</span><br />\n小弟當初差1分入a1<br />\n被教畜所害<br />\n希望日後各位多擦鞋<br />\n包住自己grade<br />\n<br />\n圖片例子為通識<br />\n我同一條友 卷一 卷二 同分<br />\nsba被佢拋離到月球<br />\n最後我4<br />\n佢5*<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你冇睇錯，係兩個大grades！</span></span><br />\n有冇跟公開試調分<br />\n自己用眼睇<br />\n<br />\n所有sba科都係如此<br />\n唯一方法就係擦鞋<br />\n<br />\n補充一句<br />\n如果通識本身非神仙級數<br />\nsba 連7/9都冇<br />\n可以收包袱啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/212850_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F212850_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d96ef4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/212907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F212907_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=205f3f89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84391e63669f813262b543e5d0d542108ef929fb","tid":459100,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"擦鞋中六擦都無用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7405035f388514695e895b046642a510034ea29","tid":459100,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"死